I have posts with many photos, I want to click on a photo, it will display modal with changing URL. I've known about how to do modal change URL in vue-router. So I've config this and this modal 
```
export const posts = {
  path: '/posts/:id',
  children: [
    { path: '/photos/:id', component: PhotoPage }
  ]
}
```
It get URL modal when I click on photo in posts: **example.com/f/2/photos/1321321** when I click a photo on a posts. But now I want to photos modal have URL: **example.com/photos/1321321**.

How can I config this? Is it children - parent routes?
